## Test-Driven Development

Changes were validated using a TDD workflow:

1. Write a failing test (`adapterRenderPath.test.ts` — FAIL)
2. Implement the adapter dispatch logic
3. Verify the test passes (`adapterRenderPath.test.ts` — PASS)

Tests live in [`tests/adapter-tests-for-integration-layer/`](./tests/adapter-tests-for-integration-layer/).

To run:
```bash
npx jest tests/adapter-tests-for-integration-layer
```

