## File Structure (Changed / Added)

```
utk_curio/
└── src/
    ├── GrammarExecutionLayer.ts        # New: central dispatch layer
    ├── GrammarAdapterRegistry.ts       # New: adapter registry
    ├── adapters/
    │   ├── VegaLiteAdapter.ts          # Extracted from useVegaLifecycle
    │   ├── UtkAdapter.ts               # Extracted from useUtkLifecycle
    │   └── D3Adapter.ts               # New: proof-of-concept D3 adapter
    └── hooks/
        └── useGrammarLifecycle.ts      # New: unified lifecycle hook

tests/
└── adapter-tests-for-integration-layer/
    └── adapterRenderPath.test.ts       # TDD tests for dispatch logic
```

