## How to Run Locally

Follow the standard [Curio usage guide](./docs/USAGE.md). No additional setup is required for the adapter pipeline — it is activated automatically for all grammar node types.

```bash
# Install dependencies
pip install utk-curio

# Or run via Docker
docker compose up
```

